org.fife.ui.rtextarea

Interface ToolTipSupplier

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LanguageAwareCompletionProvider

    public interface ToolTipSupplier
    A ToolTipSupplier can create tool tip text for an RTextArea on its behalf. A text area will check its ToolTipSupplier for a tool tip before calling the super class's implementation of JComponent.getToolTipText(). This allows applications to intercept tool tip events and provide the text for a tool tip without subclassing RTextArea.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Robert Futrell
